GHÖETIKA Season 1

GHÖ #1  •NESSA•

1. The owner of this NFT will receive a completely free digital illustration of the acquired character full body where he can appreciate it and learn more about the history and personality of his girl GHÖETIKA.
•
2. If the auction of this NFT exceeds the value of 0.50 ETH, the winner of the auction will be able to claim a physical painting of his character which will be sent anywhere in the world at no extra cost. Physical paint measurements:
60x60 CM
23.622 x 23.622 inches.
•
3.Make sure to link your email, Twitter or Instagram account to your profile so that we can contact you at the end of the auction to send you your reward for acquiring a GHÖETIKA girl.
